Enum MiniGameType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MiniGameType>
      • MiniGameType

  • public enum MiniGameType
extends java.lang.Enum<MiniGameType>
    The MiniGameType enumerable contains a value for each type of minigame the player could be required to play to defeat villains.
